To enable or disable grid snapping in [[Digital Performer]] (and to set the grid snapping values) go to the Sequence Editor ('''Project/Sequence Editor'''). The snap options are in the upper right corner of the editor. Click the note display to choose the snap value and click the box to the left of the note(s) to turn snapping on or off. (image below) 


